      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To impose enhanced penalties for conduct relating to unlawful production of a controlled substance on Federal property or while intentionally trespassing on the property of another that causes environmental damage, and for other purposes.</title>
